<p><a name="Books" id="Books"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Universal_Plug_and_Play&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: Books">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Books</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Golden_G._Richard&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Golden G. Richard (page does not exist)">Golden G. Richard</a>: <cite>Service and Device Discovery&#160;: Protocols and Programming</cite>, McGraw-Hill Professional, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0071379592" class="internal">ISBN 0-07-137959-2</a></li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Michael_Jeronimo&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Michael Jeronimo (page does not exist)">Michael Jeronimo</a>, <a href="/w/index.php?title=Jack_Weast&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Jack Weast (page does not exist)">Jack Weast</a>: <cite>UPnP Design by Example: A Software Developer's Guide to Universal Plug and Play</cite>, Intel Press, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0971786119" class="internal">ISBN 0-9717861-1-9</a></li>
</ul>
<p><a name="See_also" id="See_also"></a></p>
